PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE CLYDE K. WELLS, a Judge of Appeal of the Cour of Appeal of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland, as Chief Justice of the Court of Appeal of the Supreme Court of Newfoundland, with the style and title of Chief Justice of Newfoundland, and as a member ex officio of the Trial Division of the said Court.
